data.title: Božo Koprivica
data.meta_description: Božo Koprivica is an essayist, dramatic adviser and literary critic from Montenegro, of Yugoslavian ethnicity.
data.text:
Božo Koprivica (Serbian Cyrillic: Божо Копривица) is an essayist, dramatic adviser and literary critic from Montenegro, of Yugoslavian ethnicity.[1]
